<div id="outline-container-1.10" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="sec-1.10"><span class="section-number-3">1.10</span> This dialectic is the essential nature of&hellip; </h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-1.10">

<p>This dialectic is the essential nature of consciousness itself.
Every consciousness distinguishes that which it intends and its
own awareness of intending.
</p></div>

</div>

