<div id="outline-container-1.16" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="sec-1.16"><span class="section-number-3">1.16</span> The realm of truth is inseparably one with our&hellip; </h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-1.16">

<p>The realm of truth is inseparably one with our tentative
and provisional trials of existence; there is not a moment
of truth which is not also a shape of living consciousness.
</p></div>
